{"tid":2162433,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"延長 AppleCare 考慮期   由 60 日增加至 365 日","createTime":"2020-08-18T06:29:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T07:13:04.000Z","uid":167573,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8eb89c200fc56a4da70f70e1fbed008093ff4cc6","tid":2162433,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"到底需不需要為 Apple 產品購買 AppleCare 保障服務，相信是很多消費者買機後思前想後的事，畢竟花在 Apple 產品上的金錢不少，AppleCare 的費用亦不便宜，但假如將來有任何損壞，維修費用十分可觀。現在 Apple 終於將這個考慮期延長，讓顧客可以慢慢做決定。<br />\n<br />\n到底需不需要為 Apple 產品購買 AppleCare 保障服務，相信是很多消費者買機後思前想後的事，畢竟花在 Apple 產品上的金錢不少，AppleCare 的費用亦不便宜，但假如將來有任何損壞，維修費用十分可觀。現在 Apple 終於將這個考慮期延長，讓顧客可以慢慢做決定。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源：<a href=\"https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/216475/1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eprice.com.hk%2Fmobile%2Ftalk%2F4544%2F216475%2F1%2F&d=4FX4A6L%2BDQn5Srv%2BHBCkF51e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=4dd86c09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.eprice.com.hk/mobile/talk/4544/216475/1/</a>"},{"pid":"8c9cb8dc406e6af7c77bab148cdbe5a714512b41","tid":2162433,"uid":226739,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"點解同一段要po 兩次？"},{"pid":"d47a96688cae20301e5a4491eb2ad6e737b8027a","tid":2162433,"uid":167573,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"8c9cb8dc406e6af7c77bab148cdbe5a714512b41","tid":2162433,"uid":226739,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:30:44.000Z","msg":"點解同一段要po 兩次？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:47:26.000Z","msg":"因為post 錯....<br />\n<br />\n補反另一段先<br />\n<br />\n彭博新聞社報導指 Apple 昨日向旗下零售和客戶服務人員發通告，表示公司會將顧客考慮購買 AppleCare 的限期，由現時購買產品後 60 天內，大幅延長至一年，不過這個安排暫時只在美國和加拿大市場提供。Apple 在通告中表示此舉，可以讓顧客有更多機會保護他們的裝置，並且享用到 AppleCare 服務的好處。<br />\n<br />\n為了杜絕客戶在裝置損壞後才購買 AppleCare 服務，新安排要求顧客將裝置帶到 Apple Store 供店員作檢查，才可以在限期內購買 AppleCare 服務。暫時未知 Apple 會否把同類安排在北美以外市場推出。"},{"pid":"22676fc395adebcd54dd12dcfd3a0cf8ef74dc40","tid":2162433,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:48:19.000Z","msg":"回晒塘啦，執左佢啦"},{"pid":"10b51f06bb7d322637af6271a3024ab4fcb55449","tid":2162433,"uid":99642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:49:08.000Z","msg":"以前係一年架<br />\n有人玩串晒party"},{"pid":"b776e469a3f7413e486f2b45952390d99b4c7802","tid":2162433,"uid":25260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:49:41.000Z","msg":"我記得之前都係一年內可以買 apple care<br />\n<br />\n係 d 人濫用所以改短咗"},{"pid":"22dc95d47530fded505aecee07e562a38182c5a7","tid":2162433,"uid":261849,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T06:59:51.000Z","msg":"一年換一機 無機會買<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16008ab5be540e623bcdb69d1d424755c5f3ceb6","tid":2162433,"uid":80072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"美國同加拿大post嚟托咩<br />\n呢度係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d82cd1b47701b87f2c3f2c2ea16951b322f5883","tid":2162433,"uid":364392,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"16008ab5be540e623bcdb69d1d424755c5f3ceb6","tid":2162433,"uid":80072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:09:55.000Z","msg":"美國同加拿大post嚟托咩<br />\n呢度係中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-18T07:13:04.000Z","msg":"美水機吸引力大增<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}